description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to appoint a Porter at Clay Cross Hospital to work 35 hours per week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder is responsible for the security of the site, delivery of meals to patients, cleaning duties in both clinical and non clinical areas (further duties outlined in the job description).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The shifts include working weekends and bank holidays on a three week rota, covering from 6.30am until 8.30pm.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Barbara Greaves, 07798 732101&lt;/p&gt;
